data.description: Stunning move in ready home located in the heart of Airmont.  Newly renovated Chef's kitchen with a grand oversized island, 6 burner stove w/ griddle, double oven, sensor faucet, instant hot water, bay windows... the list goes on!  Primary bedroom with a walk in closet, newly renovated ensuite and sliders to the deck.  Vaulted ceilings, new flooring throughout the home, recessed lighting, skylights which brings ton of natural light and an impressive outdoor space with pool and firepit great for entertaining. The possibilities are endless with this property that sits on a corner lot with over 1/2 acres!!!  Great location with proximity to major highways, NJ border and shops.  A Home Protection Plan is included with the purchase!  A truly must see!!!
